         <abstract id="aspace_ebd261b690e1cd09dafc5477968e30c6">Correspondence, writings, and genealogical materials relating to the Davis and Harris families. The correspondence and writings reflect Davis' avocational activities as editor of <title render="italic">
               <part>Biblia</part>
            </title>, a journal of Oriental archeology, his interest in local Connecticut history, and his research into his wife's and his own family history.</abstract>
         <origination label="creator">
            <persname identifier="http://id.loc.gov/authorities/names/n79083584" source="naf">
               <part>Davis, Charles Henry Stanley, 1840-1917</part>
            </persname>
         </origination>
    
      </did>
